Pearsons product-moment correlation

cor.test(
  mtcars$mpg, 
  mtcars$wt,
  alternative = "two.sided",
  method = "pearson",
  conf.level = 0.95
)

Kendalls rank correlation

cor.test(
  mtcars$mpg, 
  mtcars$wt,
  alternative = "greater",
  method = "kendall",
  conf.level = 0.9,
  exact = FALSE
)
